    "source_section_latex": "\\[ \\langle a,b\\rangle = \\frac{(a+b)(a+b+1)}{2} + b. \\] Recursively pairing adjacent digits in a finite integer sequence yields a single natural number. Reducing the result modulo $153{,}600$ and adding one produces a DAANSphere address.\n\n\\[\nP_{tunnel} \\propto \\exp\\left(-\\frac{2}{\\hbar}\\int_{d_{min}}^{d_{bolt}} \\sqrt{2m_{eff}U_{barrier}(d')} \\, dd'\\right)\n\\]\n\\[\nhat{T}_{helix}(\\theta_{twist}) = \\exp\\left(-i\\frac{\\theta_{twist}}{\\lambda}\\hat{L}_z\\right)\n\\]"
